      "instruction": "<p>Cover a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>tin foil</strong> (to avoid mess!) and drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> (to prevent the fish from sticking)</p><p>Add the <strong>tandoori salmon</strong> to the baking tray[s] and put it under the grill for 6-7 min or until the fish is cooked through and starting to char</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
