    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Scrape the seeds out of the <strong>cucumber</strong> and set aside for later</p><p>Dice the <strong>cucumber</strong></p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
