    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> cucumber seeds</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and<strong> mint sauce </strong>in a mixing bowl</p><p>Season with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>mint raita</strong></p>",
