      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tandoori salmon</strong> with the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>basmati</strong> <strong>rice</strong>, <strong>kachumber salad</strong> and <strong>mint raita</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
